like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7768581bbef56f9117a9718eda53e616a6ca9af6","tid":1484802,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"全防具介紹&amp;購買連結 建議用pc開<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8v3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=f59e845a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事緣：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1482980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1482980</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPCwmq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPCwmq2.jpg&h=eff26612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPmtoHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPmtoHj.jpg&h=d25f6468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成team幫手派既人都被打擊到  覺得一定要講返件事既重點: 大家更加獨立思考<br />\n首先係我衰偷懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同大家道個歉先 朝早維園果轉 用左google form加密黎派 去到pp之後見周圍唔少人派緊就偷懶 懷疑我係鬼係合理正常  <br />\n<br />\n然後 重點 : <br />\n大家要有獨立思考     特別係好多人出左去  連登剩返唔在場既人   <br />\n拎gear有咩問題   派gear=叫你去衝?  大家會好似黑警咁冇思考能力?<br />\n<br />\n保護自已有咩問題?    一向建議連後排最少都要有單嘴3200<br />\n你永遠唔知黑警幾時會發神經 中信果班俾人射到差d窒息你有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n有合理懷疑係好 識得保護自已係好  但pp當時情況係唔少人都拎住gear幫手問<br />\n好多人都攤晒係到整理緊gear       就係因為琴日共識   今日係極多人帶晒gear出黎以防萬一 <br />\n連仔將顯示正負評延遲顯示就係唔想大家被帶風向<br />\n但點知前幾個留言原來都可以做到同樣效果  咁下次係咪又要停顯示頭一頁呢?  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好將派防具妖魔化 琴日共識都係帶fullgear. 無論咩場合保護自己先保護到旁人 帶左唔代表要做任何野 <br />\n<br />\n更加唔好提一向都話要全民防具去保護義士 <br />\n<br />\n然後有人話今日派時機唔岩 首先近期沖突期間 我地派野愈黎愈難 因為前線齊裝既比例好高 派成晚都未派晒 所以趁今日多日果時派定d俾缺某d裝既人 然後填表果邊都有講明係前線裝 拎既人都清楚佢地拎緊乜 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最尾 我地都係想每位安全 <br />\n幫我出聲既巴絲都唔洗勞氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好去返2014互屌互捉鬼 <br />\n<br />\n好多人默默付出 有用既POST 就推唔起<br />\n一D無聊捉鬼既post  就推上熱門阻住其他有用資訊  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花好多心力去幫忙 俾咁多人誤會係會hurt, but I am fine, 但下次可能會錯屌走自己人 所以大家要認真獨立思考<br />\n唔好學黑警trigger happy, 咩都噴/射左先算 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有關gear問題去返813果個post問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"認真，琴日上得連登既都係無出黎"},{"pid":"3f94138d935899d30b35a9bf092825c4313144b0","tid":1484802,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"樓主 琴晚已經見到你派野個post<br />\n見到一面倒負皮已經覺得你好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a641cca4e7dc85fe931bdee28319b3d186cee3de","tid":1484802,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7768581bbef56f9117a9718eda53e616a6ca9af6","tid":1484802,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"全防具介紹&amp;購買連結 建議用pc開<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8v3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=f59e845a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事緣：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1482980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1482980</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPCwmq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPCwmq2.jpg&h=eff26612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPmtoHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail